        <updateDate>2009-08-28T19:44:09Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Carbon Leakage Mitigation Study Act of 2009 - Directs the Secretary of Energy (DOE) to conduct studies of: (1) the risk of carbon leakage and changes in U.S. industrial output and investment resulting from the implementation of a cap-and-trade program; and (2) the impact of potential compensatory measures to prevent carbon leakage resulting from a cap-and-trade program.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
